<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Planilha Gratuita | CAIS Investimentos</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

:root{
--bg:#03101d;
--card:#082844;
--gold:#d9bd7e;
--white:#ffffff;
--text:#b8c6d3;
}

body{
font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
background:var(--bg);
color:var(--white);
overflow-x:hidden;
}

.container{
width:100%;
max-width:1400px;
margin:auto;
padding:0 40px;
}

nav{
padding:28px 0;
border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}

.logo{
height:56px;
}

.hero{
padding:90px 0;
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;
gap:70px;
align-items:center;
min-height:85vh;
}

.left h1{
font-size:72px;
line-height:1;
font-weight:600;
margin-bottom:24px;
letter-spacing:-3px;
}

.left h1 span{
display:block;
font-style:italic;
font-weight:300;
color:var(--gold);
margin-top:10px;
}

.left p{
font-size:22px;
line-height:1.7;
color:var(--text);
max-width:650px;
margin-bottom:50px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
padding:18px 34px;
background:var(--gold);
color:#03101d;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:600;
border-radius:18px;
transition:0.25s;
font-size:15px;
}

.btn:hover{
transform:translateY(-2px);
opacity:0.9;
}

.cards{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:24px;
}

.card{
background:var(--card);
border-radius:26px;
padding:38px;
display:flex;
gap:30px;
align-items:flex-start;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}

.number{
font-size:72px;
font-weight:200;
color:var(--gold);
line-height:1;
min-width:90px;
}

.card h3{
font-size:34px;
margin-bottom:10px;
font-weight:500;
}

.card p{
font-size:19px;
line-height:1.7;
color:var(--text);
}

.form-section{
padding:90px 0 120px;
}

.form-box{
background:#071d31;
padding:50px;
border-radius:30px;
max-width:820px;
margin:auto;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}

.form-box h2{
font-size:48px;
margin-bottom:14px;
}

.form-box h2 span{
color:var(--gold);
font-style:italic;
font-weight:300;
}

.form-box p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.7;
color:var(--text);
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:20px;
}

.field{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.field.full{
grid-column:1/-1;
}

label{
font-size:13px;
margin-bottom:10px;
letter-spacing:0.08em;
text-transform:uppercase;
color:#9fb2c3;
}

input,
select{
height:56px;
background:#0b2a45;
border:none;
border-radius:14px;
padding:0 18px;
font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
color:white;
font-size:16px;
outline:none;
}

select{
appearance:none;
}

button{
border:none;
cursor:pointer;
font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
}

.submit{
width:100%;
height:60px;
border-radius:16px;
background:var(--gold);
font-size:15px;
font-weight:600;
margin-top:12px;
}

footer{
padding:35px 0;
border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
text-align:center;
color:#7f93a5;
font-size:14px;
}

@media(max-width:980px){

.hero{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.left h1{
font-size:54px;
}

.card h3{
font-size:28px;
}

}

@media(max-width:700px){

.container{
padding:0 22px;
}

.hero{
padding:60px 0;
gap:40px;
}

.left h1{
font-size:42px;
}

.left p{
font-size:18px;
}

.card{
padding:28px;
}

.number{
font-size:52px;
min-width:60px;
}

.card h3{
font-size:22px;
}

.card p{
font-size:16px;
}

.form-box{
padding:30px;
}

.form-box h2{
font-size:34px;
}

.grid{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
<div class="container">
<img src="logo.png" class="logo">
</div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
<div class="container hero">

<div class="left">

<h1>
Sua direção financeira
<span>começa aqui</span>
</h1>

<p>
Você já controla. Agora vamos fazer seu dinheiro render.
Baixe gratuitamente a planilha financeira desenvolvida pela CAIS Investimentos.
</p>

<a href="#formulario" class="btn">
BAIXAR PLANILHA GRATUITA
</a>

</div>

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<div class="number">01</div>
<div>
<h3>Lance suas entradas</h3>
<p>
Salário, renda extra, aluguéis.
Tudo o que entra na sua conta no mês.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="number">02</div>
<div>
<h3>Registre suas saídas</h3>
<p>
Despesas organizadas em categorias claras.
Sem se perder em subitens.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="number">03</div>
<div>
<h3>Veja seu painel</h3>
<p>
Descubra quanto sobrou e simule quanto pode virar patrimônio nos próximos anos.
</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="form-section" id="formulario">

<div class="container">

<div class="form-box">

<h2>
Receba sua <span>planilha gratuita</span>
</h2>

<p>
Preencha os dados abaixo para liberar o acesso imediato ao download.
</p>

<form action="https://webto.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.WebToLead?encoding=UTF-8&orgId=00Das000006BB37" method="POST">

<input type="hidden" name="oid" value="00Das000006BB37">
<input type="hidden" name="retURL" value="https://SEUUSUARIO.github.io/obrigado.html">

<div class="grid">

<div class="field">
<label>Nome</label>
<input type="text" name="first_name" required>
</div>

<div class="field">
<label>Sobrenome</label>
<input type="text" name="last_name" required>
</div>

<div class="field full">
<label>WhatsApp</label>
<input type="tel" name="phone" required>
</div>

<div class="field full">
<label>E-mail</label>
<input type="email" name="email" required>
</div>

<div class="field full">
<label>Qual sua relação com investimentos?</label>

<select name="00N_RELACAO_INVESTIMENTOS" required>
<option value="">Selecione</option>
<option>Nunca investi e não entendo nada</option>
<option>Nunca investi mas entendo um pouco</option>
<option>Já investi algumas vezes</option>
<option>Já invisto e entendo do assunto</option>
</select>

</div>

<div class="field full">
<label>Quanto você possui para investir?</label>

<select name="00N_CAPITAL_DISPONIVEL" required>
<option value="">Selecione</option>
<option>Até R$ 50 mil</option>
<option>R$ 50 mil a R$ 100 mil</option>
<option>R$ 100 mil a R$ 300 mil</option>
<option>Acima de R$ 300 mil</option>
</select>

</div>

</div>

<button class="submit" type="submit">
ACESSAR PLANILHA
</button>

</form>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>
<div class="container">
© 2026 CAIS Investimentos. Todos os direitos reservados.
</div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
